snippet.title: Explore beyond Paldea's borders in The Hidden Treasure of Area Zero! 🗺️
snippet.description:
The Hidden Treasure of Area Zero Part 1: The Teal Mask launches on September 13th!

Check out the people and Pokémon you’ll meet in the upcoming Pokémon Scarlet and Pokémon Violet DLC!

Official site: http://www.pokemon.com
